resources.string: I-download at i-install ang mga karagdagang feature para sa LED View Cover. Makalilikha ka ng sarili mong mga LED icon at maise-set ang mga ito bilang mga notification icon mo. Para i-download ang mga ito sa ibang panahon, pumunta sa Settings > Advanced features > Accessories > LED view cover, tapos piliin ang Download additional features.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
